                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-2249-18370918 t18370918-2249-punishment-196"></join>Confined Three Months; Three Weeks Solitary</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Sergeant Arabin.</hi>
